      <p><strong>Ownership:</strong> Private LLC. Scott Coletti is CEO &amp; Founder (LinkedIn, ZoomInfo). The DealStream listing names "Scott L Coletti" as the contact — i.e., owner-marketed rather than handled by an independent broker.</p>
      <p><strong>Milestones:</strong> 2018 — founded, proprietary system launched. 2018–2025 — built nationwide delivery and an 8-year accident-data asset. 2025-10-13 — listed on DealStream at $5,000,000.</p>
      <p><strong>Org structure:</strong> Owner-led. Website references former Google staff and SEO-firm partnerships, but no GM/COO identified — a key-person concern.</p>
