      <p><strong>Recurring vs one-time:</strong> Predominantly recurring — flat monthly territorial retainers. Exact recurring % not disclosed but structurally subscription-based.</p>
      <p><strong>Concentration:</strong> Not disclosed. Exclusive-territory pricing creates real concentration risk in any large metro — must be confirmed with the seller.</p>
    </section>

