    <section id="risks">
      <h2>9. Risk Factors</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Industry:</strong> Heavy dependence on paid search makes lead cost/volume sensitive to Google policy and pricing; legal lead gen faces TCPA / state-bar advertising exposure.</li>
